				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">After the much welcomed and great Pet Zoning change is Suspend Minion still worth getting?
<br />

<br />
I have been following Xalmat’s Group mage recommended AA path so was wondering now our pets zone would it be best to move straight on to Spell Casting Fury until they work out how they will implement Zoning Suspend Minion.
<br />

<br />
Group Mage 
<br />

