			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">suspend minion is still usefull, yes. 
<br />
1/ traveling :
<br />
Very often we buff at a safe place, not the one where we are going to fight.
<br />
A good way to cross THE DEEP for example is to buff at entrance, invis till you meet a see invis mob, desuspend, kill, suspend, invis and go on. Much faster than killing ALL mobs till bridge.
<br />
Same in KT : group/raid meet at entrance, buff, invis and goes to fight place or to zone entrance.
<br />

<br />
2/ double pet
<br />
in some place, having a pet ready in the pocket is good to chain fastly.
<br />

<br />
3/ rez and mana
<br />
if you are in the same zone, sumon a pet, suspend, accept rez, desuspend, use pet for mana battery or fight.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=159910">
<br />
 <img border="0" src="http://www.ikebana-toulouse.com/citation/archmage.jpg" width="250" height="153">
<br />
 </a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
